<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV55">
<l>vaṇṭuka ḷōvammi ṉīrppū nilappū marattiloṇpū</l>
<l>vuṇṭu kaḷittuḻal vīrkkoṉ ṟuraikkiya mēṉamoṉṟāy</l>
<l>maṇṭuka ḷāṭivai kuntamaṉ ṉāḷkuḻal vāyviraipōl</l>
<l>viṇṭukaḷ vāru malaruḷa vōnum viyaliṭattē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Bees? Come! To you who joyfully roam about, eating from water flowers,</l>
<l>ground flowers [and] bright flowers in trees, we will tell one thing: like the scent</l>
<l>in the curls of her who is like the Vaikunta of him who bathes as a boar in earth dust,</l>
<l>are there blossoms that flow over with heavenly nectar, in your wide area?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
